00:17:02,460 --> 00:17:04,100
Well...

306
00:17:04,100 --> 00:17:05,020
Ms. Xiang

307
00:17:05,020 --> 00:17:06,190
I'm sorry.

308
00:17:06,190 --> 00:17:07,500
We're busy.

309
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:10,140
