316
00:17:30,140 --> 00:17:32,750
Make sure you interact and
communicate with each other.

317
00:17:34,060 --> 00:17:36,920
Learn and help each other.

318
00:17:40,430 --> 00:17:43,500
What a combination! Just like
the lucky draw of the lottery!

319
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:44,390
What did you say?

320
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:45,080
Oh!

321
00:17:46,130 --> 00:17:48,370
I mean you're so wise.

322
00:17:48,370 --> 00:17:50,450
I like drama the most.

323
00:17:50,860 --> 00:17:52,000
That's great!

324
00:17:53,190 --> 00:17:54,090
Good!

325
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:57,730
As Feng Shao said,
the 8th strategy of the tips,

326
00:17:57,730 --> 00:17:59,400
"A Cool CEO".

