00:17:59,400 --> 00:18:02,780
Do not give her a smile.

328
00:18:02,780 --> 00:18:04,440
Must let her understand that

329
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:05,800
you don't care about her.

330
00:18:05,890 --> 00:18:07,790
And you hate her very much.

331
00:18:07,790 --> 00:18:09,350
Chill her and provoke her...

332
00:18:09,350 --> 00:18:10,190
Today,

333
00:18:10,330 --> 00:18:12,980
we'll rehearse a sequence from Pride and Prejudice

334
00:18:12,980 --> 00:18:16,010
