341
00:18:41,650 --> 00:18:43,540
to other students.

342
00:18:43,980 --> 00:18:44,550
Okay.

343
00:18:45,110 --> 00:18:45,870
Very good.

344
00:18:46,420 --> 00:18:47,480
In that case,

345
00:18:47,610 --> 00:18:50,100
